let you know that Karlijn Dinnissen will present and discuss our joint paper &lt;a href="https://chbeu.github.io/publications/dinnissen-2022-fairness-in-music-recommender-systems">Fairness in music recommender systems: a stakeholder-centered mini review&lt;/a> at the &lt;a href="https://facctrec.github.io/facctrec2022/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">5th FAccTRec Workshop: Responsible Recommendation&lt;/a> at &lt;a href="https://recsys.acm.org/recsys22/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">RecSys 2022&lt;/a>.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>In the &lt;a href="https://arxiv.org/abs/2209.06126" target="_blank" rel="noopener">FAcctRec abstract&lt;/a>, we summarize the main findings and point to the two open questions (arising from the review) that we will address at the workshop.&lt;/p>
